{"tid":551662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不服務中共  最大網絡水軍遭封殺  付350元可發5,000個post","createTime":"2018-02-06T01:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T02:56:33.000Z","uid":136994,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e01755b34505089c0f2d6a9d1692f1c45f655dcd","tid":551662,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:06:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180206/20296586?_ga=2.90482458.1886174960.1517808856-575505850.1502150827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F20296586%3F_ga%3D2.90482458.1886174960.1517808856-575505850.1502150827&d=oP%2FjWudc8YgxXNjUVbh7MDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=06e56756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F20296586%3F_ga%3D2.90482458.1886174960.1517808856-575505850.1502150827&h=76bf8db7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180206/20296586?_ga=2.90482458.1886174960.1517808856-575505850.1502150827</a><br />\n<br />\n中共大力培植自己網絡「水軍」同時，全力打壓異己。新華社昨披露公安去年以來打擊「網絡水軍」成績時，特別揭露其中一支叫「三打哈」的網絡水軍內幕，指該水軍遍佈21省市，是內地最大利用網絡進行非法活動的集團。有評論直指，私人水軍不服務官方，故當局要殺一儆百。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，「三打哈」網站2016年7月成立，屬內地大型水軍中介平台。網民在網站註冊成「僱主」發佈任務，就有水軍接單工作。水軍從事有償刪帖、誹謗攻擊、非法推廣等。遇到對僱主不利消息，水軍會當中介，利誘目標論壇版主或技術人員當內鬼刪帖。通常刪一帖索價300至500元人民幣（下同，約378至623港元）。<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹：當局殺一儆百<br />\n若無法利誘版主配合，水軍則在帖內發佈色情相片，令該帖「違規」，逼版主不得不自己刪帖。水軍亦收錢從事誹謗攻擊或非法推廣，透過時事熱話牽動網民情緒，造勢宣傳僱主；由於詆毀對手比宣傳自己更有效，助長水軍無所不用其極。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">公安形容，只要有錢水軍甚麼都敢發，最低350元（436港元）可發5,000條短訊或帖子</span>，內容敏感帖子收費更高。「三打哈」更掌握內地500萬條公民個人訊息，覆蓋全國多21個省分，能按目標特性發放訊息，務求最大成效。本案涉案金額上億元，最少200人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹對《蘋果》指，私人水軍「只服務客人不服務官方」，加上「三打哈」越做越大可能失控或造成混亂，今次是殺一儆百。不過官方也與網絡水軍合作，水軍不會完全被消滅，但可能收斂一段時間後故態復萌。自去年5月當局開展網絡水軍打擊行動以來，共拘捕200多人，關閉5000多個賬號、上萬個違規網站。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪要改口做「一毛黨」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0991c1fdecf53682a7cfcc9f8482a337a50f9f8e","tid":551662,"uid":116530,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"而家連五毛都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133f87b1c4b69c9d770dd1e94b6e0bb2d46b377c","tid":551662,"uid":164167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0991c1fdecf53682a7cfcc9f8482a337a50f9f8e","tid":551662,"uid":116530,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"而家連五毛都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:12:26.000Z","msg":"鬥爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97407e327004f8d3666c6df91b0bf0babcfdcdcc","tid":551662,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0991c1fdecf53682a7cfcc9f8482a337a50f9f8e","tid":551662,"uid":116530,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"而家連五毛都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"已經可以AI 代替"},{"pid":"a8438959ed81268ea4b8ca0b1f64afd2327abe3d","tid":551662,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0991c1fdecf53682a7cfcc9f8482a337a50f9f8e","tid":551662,"uid":116530,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"而家連五毛都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"一毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ed787e54737df46634a2775fabbbfca1328b2a","tid":551662,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:31:02.000Z","msg":"原來我地叫打手，上面叫水軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\